        "synopsis": {
            "value": "Han Jun-Hee’s (Jeon Yeo-Bin) boyfriend Koo Yeon-Jun (Ahn Hyo-Seop) died 1 year ago. She still hasn't gotten over the death of her boyfriend and misses him a lot.\n\nOne day, she somehow travels back in time to the year 1998 and finds herself as high school student Kwon Min-Ju (Jeon Yeo-Bin). At school, she meets high school student Nam Si-Heon (Ahn Hyo-Seop). She is surprised that Nam Si-Heon resembles so much her late boyfriend Koo Yeon-Jun. Nam Si-Heon is an outgoing person and physically attractive. He is adored by the female students. Meanwhile, Jung-In-Gyu (Kang Hoon) is best friends with Nam Si-Heon and develops a crush on Kwon Min-Ju.",
            "source": "asianwiki",
            "source_link": "https://asianwiki.com/A_Time_Called_You"
